TI  - Development of a GIS coastal land-use planning tool for coastal erosion adaptation based on the exposure of buildings and infrastructure to coastal erosion, Quebec, Canada
JO  - Geomatics Natural Hazards \& Risk
PY  - 2017
VL  - 8
